svg.source:
title: User OnBoarding flow
Merchant->Backend: startRegistration(aadhar, shopkeeper Id)
Merchant->User: <request fingerprint>
User->Merchant: <provides fingerprint>
Merchant->Aadhar_system: <aadhar Auth>
Aadhar_system->Merchant: <Auth data, Auth Id>
Merchant->Backend: registerUser(aadhar, shopkeeper Id, authData, user_type)
Backend->Core_Banking: <request user data by aadhar auth>
Core_Banking->Backend: <user data including registered mobile number>
Backend->Merchant: <OTP once the registered mobile number is known>
Merchant->User: <Requests user to send SMS>
User->SMS_Gateway: <SMS with OTP>
SMS_Gateway->Backend: verifyRegistrationWithUser(otp, aadhar number)
Backend->Ledger_API: createUserAccount(userId, authId, user_public_key, user_type)
Ledger_API->Backend: response contains private key of user
Backend->SMS_Gateway: sendRegistrationAlert(userId, aadhar_number, status)
SMS_Gateway->User: <registration status message>
Backend->Merchant: <response to createUser>
Ledger_API->*User_Contract: <user data, user public key, Auth Id, user_type, shopAddress>
User_Contract->*Bank_Account_Contract: < user address >
Bank_Account_Contract->User_Contract: <update bank account address>
User_Contract->*Reputation_Contract: < user address >
Reputation_Contract->User_Contract: <update reputation contract address>
User_Contract->Shop_Reputation_Contract: changeReputation(changeType)
Reputation_Contract->Backend: <event that reputation contract is created>
Bank_Account_Contract->Backend: < event that bank account is created>
User_Contract->Backend: <event that user contract is created>
Backend->Merchant: <registration status, private_key>
Backend->SMS_Gateway: sendRegistrationAlert(userId, aadhar_number, status)
SMS_Gateway->User: <registration status message>
